">粉红色可卡因</a>”（一种通常由甲基苯丙胺，氯胺酮，MDMA等物质组成的药物，以及他的系统中的可卡因，苯二氮卓和裂缝。报道还称，从他当时入住的酒店房间中发现了一根临时铝管。</p><p>据报道，布宜诺斯艾利斯警察局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-payne-died-3806078">突袭了卡萨苏尔酒店，以寻求进一步的证据</a>。</p><p>佩恩（Payne）的去世引发了关于对年轻艺术家提供更多保护的对话，词曲作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">盖伊·钱伯斯（Guy Chambers）呼吁音乐行业停止在他去世后停止将未成年人送入男女乐队</a>。佩恩（Payne）第一次参加<em>X因子</em>时，他是14岁，在节目的第十个赛季成为一个方向的成员时，他是16岁。</p><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Sharon-Osbourne">沙龙·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne）</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-accuses-music-industry-of-letting-down-liam-payne-3803983">指责音乐行业“让失望”的佩恩（Payne</a> ）在Instagram帖子中写道：“ Liam，我的心很酸。我们都让你失望。当您需要时，这个行业在哪里？当您进入世界上最艰难的行业之一时，您只是个孩子。谁在你的角落？我的朋友安息。” </p><figure id="attachment_3805683" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805683" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805683" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805683" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩。图片来源：安德鲁·钦/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Katie-Waissel">凯蒂·沃塞尔（Katie Waissel</a> ）在人才展上与一个方向并肩作战，此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katie-waissel-calls-for-more-care-and-support-for-young-artists-after-death-of-liam-payne-the-focus-remained-on-profits-rather-than-the-people-3803888">呼吁更多“照顾和支持年轻艺术家</a>”。同样，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森（Rebecca Ferguson）</a>在演出的同一个赛季排名第二，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rebecca-ferguson-speaks-out-on-exploitation-and-profiteering-of-young-stars-in-liam-payne-tribute-3803708">向佩恩致敬，同时也反对“年轻明星的剥削和利润”。</a></p><p>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）还说，在佩恩（Payne）死后，音乐行业对年轻人施加了巨大的压力<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Victoria-Canal">维多利亚运河（Victoria Canal</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">“这个行业&#39;成功&#39;的希望是什么。”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132">此后，启动了一份新的请愿书，呼吁制定一项新法律，以维护音乐行业艺术家的心理健康</a>。请愿书已超过100,000个签名。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kate-cassidy-leaving-liam-payne-alone-in-argentina-before-his-death-will-haunt-her-for-the-rest-of-her-life-3806450">凯特·卡西迪（Kate Cassidy）在他去世之前就离开了利亚姆·佩恩（Liam Payne）独自一人在阿根廷人“困扰她一生”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
